Lipinski, Pulitzer Prize winner when the Tribune

00:21:02.879 --> 00:21:13.879
was winning Pulitzer Prizes instead of being
in bankruptcy. I was fortunate to serve and

00:21:13.879 --> 00:21:22.070
then become chairman of the Carnegie Foundation
which was a basic funder for a public broadcasting.

00:21:22.070 --> 00:21:28.289
So I ve had a blessed, fortunate life but
the most important thing that I want to urge

00:21:28.289 --> 00:21:36.179
a discussion about today is the future, not
the past. Thomas Jefferson said he liked the

00:21:36.179 --> 00:21:41.669
