00:21:41.669 --> 00:21:47.960
world. My grandchildren tell me they don t
even have television sets. What they watched

00:21:47.960 --> 00:21:56.989
is on their computer. You can carry your iPad
around and see what s going on. The internet

00:21:56.989 --> 00:22:05.259
is absolutely one of the most important inventions
of all time. There again I was lucky. I was

00:22:05.259 --> 00:22:11.330
on the board of the Rand Corporation when
the first work was done to create the internet

00:22:11.330 --> 00:22:18.269
under a contract for the government. People
forget this. The government funded what is

00:22:18.269 --> 00:22:25.179
today we call the internet. There was a contract
led up by the Department of Defense and Rand

00:22:25.179 --> 00:22:31.840
developed what s called packet switching and
that now is the guts of enabling the internet

